MaintainPeriodForm is a CompositeForm
    title is "ClosePeriod<ClosePeriod.CloseCalendarPeriod>_<ClosePeriod.CloseCalendar>is<CloseManagementStatus>"
    restrict action Create
    restrict action Update
    Actions
        action is OpenPeriod
            label is "Open"
            hide when invalid
        action is CloseThePeriod
            label is "Close"
            hide when invalid
        action is ReopenPeriod
            label is "Reopen"
            hide when invalid
        action is Reset
            label is "Reset"
            hide when invalid
        action is RevertToScheduled
            label is "Reset"
            hide when invalid
        action is SendMessage
        action is Reminder
        action is WorkRequest
    AtAGlance is a Panel
        form is PeriodAtAGlanceForm
    ReopenAudit is a Panel
        visible when (PeriodReopened)
        list is audit log records.ReopenAuditLogList
    TheClose is a Panel
        list is TheClose.primary
    Issue is a Panel
        visible when (IssueExists)
        list is PeriodIssueRel.primary
